	<h2>Commercial Fencing Code Compliance</h2>

	<h3>California Building Code Requirements</h3>
	<p><strong>Commercial Fencing Standards:</strong> Commercial fencing must meet more stringent requirements than residential:</p>

	<ul>
		<li><strong>Wind Load:</strong> Must be engineered for 85 mph wind loads (Exposure C) in Stockton</li>
		<li><strong>Structural Design:</strong> Professional engineering may be required for fences over 6 feet</li>
		<li><strong>Foundation:</strong> Concrete footings sized per soil conditions and fence height/type</li>
		<li><strong>Setbacks:</strong> Typically 5-10 feet from property line for commercial properties</li>
		<li><strong>Fire Safety:</strong> Separation requirements near buildings, combustible material restrictions</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Stockton Municipal Code Compliance</h3>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Height Limits:</strong> Typically 8 feet maximum without variance (some zones different)</li>
		<li><strong>Sight Distance:</strong> Height restrictions at driveways and intersections (typically 30-inch max in visibility triangles)</li>
		<li><strong>Screening Requirements:</strong> Dumpsters, equipment, outdoor storage must be screened</li>
		<li><strong>Barbed Wire Restrictions:</strong> Generally prohibited in commercial zones except industrial areas, must be 6+ feet high</li>
		<li><strong>Electric Fence:</strong> Prohibited in most commercial zones without special permits</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>ADA (Americans with Disabilities Act) Compliance</h3>
	<p><strong>Critical ADA Requirements for Commercial Fencing:</strong></p>

	<ul>
		<li><strong>Accessible Routes:</strong> Gates must provide 32-inch minimum clear width when open 90 degrees</li>
		<li><strong>Opening Force:</strong> Gate operating force maximum 5 pounds</li>
		<li><strong>Hardware Height:</strong> Latches and locks between 34-48 inches from ground</li>
		<li><strong>Maneuvering Space:</strong> Level areas before/after gates (60x60 inch minimum)</li>
		<li><strong>Automatic Gates:</strong> Must have manual override for emergency/power failure</li>
		<li><strong>Surface:</strong> Firm, stable, slip-resistant surfaces in gate areas</li>
	</ul>

