	<p><strong>Cannabis Facilities:</strong> California Bureau of Cannabis Control security requirements (8-foot minimum, video surveillance integration, limited access points)</p>

	<p><strong>Medical Facilities:</strong> HIPAA privacy considerations for outdoor areas, emergency access requirements</p>

	<p><strong>Schools/Daycare:</strong> California Department of Social Services licensing requirements, child safety standards</p>

